<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٤٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3997">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ: </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2330">سَعِيدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَمَّا فُتِحَتْ خَيْبَرُ أُهْدِيَتْ لِرَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> شَاةٌ فِيهَا سُمٌّ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>